{{Italic title}} {{Infobox website | name = ''MadameNoire'' | logo = | screenshot = | caption = | url = {{url|madamenoire.com}} | commercial = | type = [[Online magazine]] | language = English | registration = | owner = | author = | launch date = 2010 | alexa = | current status = Active | revenue = }} '''''MadameNoire''''' is an international [[online magazine]] that is geared toward the lifestyles of [[African Americans|African American women]] as well as [[popular culture]].
